{
  "stem": "5261.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then for some Polish friends, even from in the school, they joked, oh, you look like a Jew.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because me, I looked exactly like my mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in-- in Torun, we had not so many Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had some restaurants-- Jewish restaurants.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had some storehouses.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember that we made the shopping by the-- by [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Leiser. ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Leiser-- ?] [? it ?] was very nice quality dealer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he gave us-- not at cash, even for a few months at the rate to pay it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was very good condition.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the two boys in my school-- I don't know now the names-- they were also very good-- were very good friendship.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I never forget when the war began.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then-- when we have seen synagogue was burned and all books-- prayer books were burned.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one of them, he said, you see?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Just now they started with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe tomorrow they will start with you in the same way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Was there a synagogue in Torun?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But whether the synagogue is still now, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because after the war, where I return to Poland-- later, you see-- my contact with Torun was very-- very seldom-- only from time to time.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I didn't visit those places, even the places where I was arrested, where I have the very bad war experience, even this place where I met somebody-- I didn't go.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't see the place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, in my country was-- in my place in Torun, it was excellent.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As I told you, there were some Jewish restaurant.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Me, as a child-- because I had to work always during my holiday-- school holidays-- by German gardener or by Jew restaurants.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
